*Kapiram* da je njegov problem veliki.(I understand that his problem is big.)

On *kapira* da se nešto sprema.(He understands that something is being prepared.)

Deca *kapiraju* da su zakoni bitni.(Children understand that laws are important.)

Oni *kapiraju* da im je pomoć potrebna.(They understand that they need help.)

Ona *kapira* da je za nju bolje da ode.(She understands that it's better for her to leave.)

*Kapiramo* da znamo da znamo da ne znamo.(We understand that we know that we don't know.)